00:01:30.299 --> 00:01:34.229
border line of being a fish eye but not really
a fish eye because there is a magnification

00:01:34.229 --> 00:01:39.209
factor and a digital thing and it is 1.5 but
that is for another time in store. But it

00:01:39.209 --> 00:01:42.649
pretty much gives me the ability to shoot
wide angle shots. If you ever see those shots

00:01:42.649 --> 00:01:46.659
you could see way to the left and way to the
right and everything in the middle is pushed

00:01:46.659 --> 00:01:50.469
